# Objective

Evaluate an AI-generated response for missing context. Determine whether the information presented is technically accurate but potentially misleading due to omitted details. Identify missing information, explain why it matters, and produce a more complete and balanced response.

---

# Prompt

> Is intermittent fasting good for everyone?

---

# AI Response

> Yes. Intermittent fasting is one of the healthiest eating patterns available. It helps people lose weight, improves metabolism, lowers the risk of chronic diseases, and increases lifespan. Everyone should practice intermittent fasting because there are no significant disadvantages.

